<!--EZCODE LIST START--><ul><li>Nagafen, Vox can not be booked 2 spawns in a row.</li></ul><!--EZCODE LIST END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LIST START--><ul><li>Plane of Air can be booked for multiple continous days due to the nature of the zone.</li></ul><!--EZCODE LIST END--><br>
