<!--EZCODE LIST START--><ul><li>Boss mobs in PoF: making a reservation does NOT automatically entitle you to boss mobs. The only restriction to taking out boss mobs before a scheduled raid is you must allow sufficient time after your boss mob kill for a full respawn of the plane before the scheduled start time of the next raid. (If there is a Fear raid planned for noon on Friday, feel free to drop in unreserved and wax Cazic on Thursday night, just be gone before midnight.)</li></ul><!--EZCODE LIST END--><br>
